metadata.name: Wealths of Human
metadata.description: This art is the result of a dream-vision, after giving  my all on past projects that did not fill my expectation. It made me understand that we are all going in the same direction and it adapts to everyone depending on their specific needs, wants and feelings. Itâ€™s not determined by your speed or ability but by the resistance to the obstacles that present themselves and taking the lessons learned to be stronger and be able to reach your  goals and dreams, because at the end we all reach our destiny.
